data.description: If you're looking for convenient country living, look no further! This custom single story brick home is situated on just shy of 20 acres located within a couple miles from downtown Aiken and all of your shopping necessities. One of the unique things about this property is it is right outside the city line and has no restrictions but has city water and septic with city sewer available. This property has been fenced for horses but fully suitable for really any livestock you may desire to have with feeding sheds and horse stalls. This home is 4-bedrooms, 3=bath with a large family room/sunroom with a vaulted ceiling with large windows that bring in adequate natural light & provides a great view of the fenced in backyard. The sunroom flows to the kitchen that has granite countertops and overlooks the formal living & dining area. Master suite has dual sinks & a walk-in shower in the bathroom. Two bedrooms share the hall bath, & the fourth bedroom is split with its own private full bathroom. This home has a 2-car attached garage as well as a detached 2,000 sqft 4 bay garage/workshop with electricity & water. Outside you will also find a sprinkler system with its own separate well. This property is located within 30 minutes of Augusta, Georgia and the savannah river. Less than an hour from Columbia SC, Lake Murray, & Clark Hill Lake. Don't miss out on this great opportunity!
